Package fi.tuni.olvander.citybicyclejourneys.stations

Class Station

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.olvander.citybicyclejourneys.stations.Station
@Entity public class Station extends Object
A Station class, that is used when Station objects are added to the
Station database and for getting Station related data.
Since:
1.21
Version:
2023.12.13
Author:
Olli Pertovaara
